{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/TIL_7_210107/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"views\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#views\" aria-label=\"views permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>views</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>뜻 : 화면에 표시되는 모든 것이 view </li>\n<li>\n<p>예시</p>\n<ul>\n<li>텍스트</li>\n<li>슬라이더</li>\n<li>버튼</li>\n<li>\n<p>VStack(Vertical Stack)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>view의 일종으로, 다른 view들을 담는 container 역할</li>\n<li>Vertically 담음</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>HStack</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Horizontally 담음</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"swift-view-modifiers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#swift-view-modifiers\" aria-label=\"swift view modifiers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Swift View Modifiers</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>뜻 : CSS같은 개념. UI적 요소들을 바꿀 수 있음</li>\n<li>규칙 : View modifier가 적힌 순서대로 코드가 적용된다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>예시 : 아래 예시에서, border에는 opacity가 적용 안됨</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Text(&quot;100&quot;)\n.opacity(0.5)\n.border(color.red, width: 2)</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"modifers-유의사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#modifers-%EC%9C%A0%EC%9D%98%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-label=\"modifers 유의사항 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Modifers 유의사항</h3>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>각 modifer가 return하는 view 종류가 다르다</p>\n<ul>\n<li>예를 들어, .bold() -> Text view를 리턴</li>\n<li>하지만 lineSpacing()은 그냥 view를 리턴</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>때문에 modifier를 놓는 순서를 잘 고려해야 함. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>bold를 lineSpacing에 놓으면, 안됨. bold는 text view에 적용해야하는 것이라</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"modifier1---font\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#modifier1---font\" aria-label=\"modifier1   font permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Modifier(1) - font()</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>font size를 하드코딩 하는게 아니라, title, footnote 등의 속성으로 해두면 화면 크기에 따라 size를 조정해줌</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"modifier1---kerning\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#modifier1---kerning\" aria-label=\"modifier1   kerning permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Modifier(1) - kerning()</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>기능 : letter spacing</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"기타\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80\" aria-label=\"기타 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기타</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>ctrl + cmmd + space : 이모지 창\n</li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"views 뜻 : 화면에 표시되는 모든 것이 view  예시 텍스트 슬라이더 버튼 VStack(Vertical Stack) view의 일종으로, 다른 view들을 담는 container 역할 Vertically 담음 HStack Horizontall…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_7_210107/#views\">views</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_7_210107/#swift-view-modifiers\">Swift View Modifiers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_7_210107/#%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80\">기타</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/TIL_7_210107/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TIL_210107","date":"Jan 07, 2021","tags":["TIL","swift"],"keywords":["dobedh","Donghyun Kim"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/TIL_7_210107/","series":[],"lastmod":"2021-01-07"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}